RT @PatrioticMills: It's time for the ultra-wealthy to step up.

Member, Alan Davis, encourages them to sign the Crisis Charitable Commitment. Signing on means agreeing to contribute a minimum of $100,000 to nonprofits in 2020 or a minimum % of net worth.

